                "invention-title": [
                    "Low-cost and water-saving system for preparing methanol from natural gas",
                    "一种低成本、节水型天然气制甲醇系统"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a low-cost and water-saving system for preparing methanol from natural gas. The low-cost and water-saving system comprises a natural gas combined conversion system, a methanol synthesis rectification system and a process condensate steam stripping system. Compared with traditional combined conversion (steam conversion (SMR) and ATR conversion) under the same product scale, the same water-carbon ratio and the same operation condition, the stoichiometric ratio ((H2-CO2)/(CO + CO2)) required by methanol synthesis of fresh gas can be flexibly adjusted by arranging a large pre-conversion and steam conversion (SMR) bypass or a small steam conversion (SMR) bypass, and hydrogen does not need to be additionally supplemented; a hydrogen recovery unit does not need to be arranged, and the thermal load of the steam reforming furnace can be effectively reduced by arranging the bypass, so that the size of the steam reforming furnace is reduced. And meanwhile, the steam conversion load with lower heat efficiency is reduced, so that the heat efficiency of the whole device is improved, and the amount of byproduct high-pressure steam is reduced, thereby reducing the load required by steam overheating, and further reducing the size of an overheating coil pipe of the steam conversion furnace and the size of a high-pressure steam pipeline system."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种低成本、节水型天然气制甲醇系统，包括：天然气组合式转化系统、甲醇合成精馏系统和工艺冷凝液汽提系统。本发明在相同产品规模，相同水碳比及操作条件下与传统组合式转化(蒸汽转化(SMR)+ATR转化)相比，通过设置预转化+蒸汽转化(SMR)大旁路或蒸汽转化(SMR)小旁路可灵活调节甲醇合成新鲜气所需要的化学计量比((H2‑CO2)/(CO+CO2))，不需要额外补入氢气，即不需要设置氢回收单元，通过设置旁路可以有效降低蒸汽转化炉热负荷，从而减少蒸汽转化炉的尺寸。同时因为降低了热效率较低的蒸汽转化负荷，使得整体装置热效率提高，并减少副产高压蒸汽量，从而减少了蒸汽过热所需负荷，进一步减少了蒸汽转化炉过热盘管的尺寸和高压蒸汽管道系统的大小。"
                }
            ]
